          <li>Scores the <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">impact</strong> (<a href="/scoring/" class="text-[var(--color-accent-primary)] hover:underline">NISS vulnerability scoring</a>)</li>
          <li>Builds the <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">defenses</strong> (<a href="/tools/" class="text-[var(--color-accent-primary)] hover:underline">Neurowall, NSP, Runemate</a>)</li>
          <li>Answers how to detect, prevent, and respond technically</li>
        </ul>
