      <p class="mb-4">
        This landscape survey draws from 255+ verified research sources compiled in the
        <a href="https://github.com/qinnovates/qinnovate/blob/main/qif-framework/QIF-RESEARCH-SOURCES.md"
           class="text-[var(--color-accent-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          QIF Research Sources Registry
        </a>.
        All citations have been verified via DOI resolution or publisher URL. See Sections 11, 11b, and 11c
        for the full neuroethics bibliography.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-faint)]">
        Survey conducted 2026-03-04 by 6 parallel research agents covering: Columbia, Stanford, Harvard/MIT, UPenn/Duke,
        Europe (ETH Zurich, Oxford, Freiburg, Uppsala/HBP, Council of Europe), and JHU/Brown/International bodies
